#. type: multicols
#: coops/close_to_enemies.tex:9
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textit{``Sir! The raiders are at our gates!''}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\textit{``Herr! Die Plünderer stehen vor unseren Toren!''}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: coops/close_to_enemies.tex:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textit{``Sound the warhorn! We'll drive them back as always!'' you command, and go to defend the city. Just as you have done many times before. Such is the harsh life of the border clans, where wars and skirmishes with neighboring rivals never truly end. Fortunately, your alliance remains strong, and you know your back is covered.}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\textit{„Blast das Kriegshorn! Wir werden sie zurückschlagen, wie immer!“, befiehlst du und widmest dich der Verteidigung der Stadt. So wie du es schon mehrere Male getan hast. Dies ist das harte Leben der Grenzclans, wo Kriege und Scharmützel mit benachbarten Rivalen nie wirklich enden. Glücklicherweise bleibt deine Allianz stark, und du weißt, dass du auf der sicheren Seite bist.}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: coops/close_to_enemies.tex:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textit{The time has come to end these long-standing wars and crush your enemies like a bug once and for all!}\n"
"% Translator info: In Homam IV was Quote like: \"Rufux will crush this army like a bug.\" If has scounting and has bigger army. So \"like a bug\" is little easter egg referencing on this.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\textit{Die Zeit ist gekommen, diese langjährigen Kriege zu beenden und eure Gegner endlich wie Käfer zu zerquetschen!}\n"
"% Translator info: In Homam IV was Quote like: \"Rufux will crush this army like a bug.\" If has scounting and has bigger army. So \"like a bug\" is little easter egg referencing on this.\n"
"\n"

